    "description": "Take the role of the army commander for the habitants of Nardia. Strategically navigate your way through the hordes of undead by building your perfect army to achieve victory in this roguelike auto battle simulator. Refine your tactics, use magic, upgrade your fighters, and make your way through the tech tree to unlock even more powers and upgrades to defeat the undead.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/81749d9ace49f56888149dd1c4cb0157.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=159 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/1971ed39506af6fd01ba8f11ccd1bbe4.poster.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/1971ed39506af6fd01ba8f11ccd1bbe4.webm?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/1971ed39506af6fd01ba8f11ccd1bbe4.mp4?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Lead your chosen race to victory, with each race having their own spell powers that have both strengths and weaknesses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/f283cd12742826d7c48cdee588885e51.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=159 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/b2e79066ca2d762d92ed1e87c56c0fc8.poster.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/b2e79066ca2d762d92ed1e87c56c0fc8.webm?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/b2e79066ca2d762d92ed1e87c56c0fc8.mp4?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Strategically choosing your fighters and their position on the battlefield ​will greatly affect your chance of victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/5a107aff38d2b2941094fd8605a2843b.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=159 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/942ee5416bfff84dd2dc1fb69f6106b9.poster.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/942ee5416bfff84dd2dc1fb69f6106b9.webm?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/942ee5416bfff84dd2dc1fb69f6106b9.mp4?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Earn Dark souls and spend them on persistent rewards in the upgrade tree to maximize your chance of victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/801bf1ad18e8056b044f8f2c27ba2fb4.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=159 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/982fb9078fcd066f5f8ac08d52349f91.poster.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/982fb9078fcd066f5f8ac08d52349f91.webm?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/982fb9078fcd066f5f8ac08d52349f91.mp4?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose from unique spells and powers to help your army on the battlefield.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/5e697e2b30fd03742f834b184dfa53fb.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=159 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/a658095aac5748f03e2d088b51cc7b1f.poster.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/a658095aac5748f03e2d088b51cc7b1f.webm?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/a658095aac5748f03e2d088b51cc7b1f.mp4?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>For your fun and replayability.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/15de3756e687c1c25a972647a6ecb211.poster.avif?t=1704322554\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/15de3756e687c1c25a972647a6ecb211.webm?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276620/extras/15de3756e687c1c25a972647a6ecb211.mp4?t=1704322554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
